00:27:37,700 --> 00:27:39,009
I do.

514
00:27:39,535 --> 00:27:42,555
I got something in
the box over there.

515
00:27:49,920 --> 00:27:51,147
HUGH: Jade.

516
00:27:52,590 --> 00:27:53,732
Sorry.

517
00:27:58,804 --> 00:28:00,906
So, I spoke with Dr. Fitzgerald.

518
00:28:01,390 --> 00:28:02,724
- Mmm-hmm.
- And we set a breakfast

519
00:28:02,725 --> 00:28:03,993
for the morning you start.

520
00:28:04,060 --> 00:28:06,745
You know, just so you can spend
that little extra time with her.

521
00:28:07,438 --> 00:28:09,373
- Okay.
- Yeah.

522
00:28:10,441 --> 00:28:12,251
And the dorm's all arranged?

523
00:28:12,276 --> 00:28:14,462
I move in not this
Sunday, but next.

524
00:28:15,654 --> 00:28:17,047
(CHUCKLES)

525
00:28:19,075 --> 00:28:20,926
(CAR ENGINE STARTS)

